{"tid":1338221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"干諾道中近康樂廣場 要人！","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T13:01:47.000Z","uid":88420,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2638a763dfba6bc30ad850d908b6cf8a9a21f538","tid":1338221,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjjR3jQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjjR3jQ.png&h=97390b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦現正清場<br />\n大家未必埋到去<br />\n仲有可能影響到前面手足撤退<br />\n過左信德中心之後仲有好一段腳程<br />\n<br />\n反而康樂廣場對開完全無人<br />\n呢個位每日繁忙時間都好多車好多巴士經過<br />\n只要圍封到 IFC 至 大會堂嘅干諾道中<br />\n我地就贏一半㗎啦<br />\n而且附近有船有地鐵有半山<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好淨係出西環<br />\n係時候留少少力翻中環！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不撤不散！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936a31874cea25dee9ad3415d7986a3c04143bc2","tid":1338221,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7ob3nb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7ob3nb.png&h=0fdeed8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個中環都無人<br />\n如果狗狗係灣仔進攻<br />\n上環同埋西環嘅兄弟姐妹會好危險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b355ef0c10bba39a935b22c464a58fddac8d7e","tid":1338221,"uid":88420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一齊 be water!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567380df12f83f732fde021ed52f5f3ea7d2f4fc","tid":1338221,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"Sorry for push again<br />\n中環需要更多人 <